\id 1PE - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020 
\h 1 Petro 
\toc1 Petro Mokwongo 
\toc2 1 Petro 
\toc3 1Pet 
\mt1 1 Petro 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 An Petro ma jaote Yesu Kristo, 
\b  
\p Andikonu un jo-Nyasaye moyiero ma gin welo e piny, kendo mokere kuonde duto mag Ponto, gi Galatia, gi Kapadokia, gi Asia kod Bithinia.  
\v 2 Nyasaye Wuoro noyierou chon kaka dwarone obet mondo opwodhu gi Roho, umak chik Yesu Kristo kendo mondo rembe okir kuomu. 
\b  
\p Ngʼwono kod kwe mogundho obed kodu. 
\b  
\s1 Pak ni Nyasaye kuom geno mangima 
\p  
\v 3 Duongʼ obed ne Nyasaye ma wuon Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo nikech kuom kechne maduongʼ, osenywolwa manyien mi wayudo geno mangima kuom chier mane Yesu Kristo ochiergo oa kuom joma otho.  
\v 4 Mano emomiyo wabedo gi geno mangima mar yudo mwandu mosiko ma okanonu e polo malo kuma ok onyal kethore kata lalie.  
\v 5 Kuom yie Nyasaye oserito jogo gi tekone nyaka chop warruok moseiki mondo ofweny chiengʼ giko.  
\v 6 Beduru mamor kuom wachni, kata obedo ni sani pod uneno sand mopogore opogore kuom kinde matin.  
\v 7 Gik makamagi osetimorenu mondo one ane ka un gi yie mar adier. To Kata mana dhahabu manyalo kethore bende ipwodho gi mach. Omiyo yie maru ma nengone tek moloyo dhahabu, nyaka tem mondo ongʼego ka en yie mar adier. Eka unuyud pak kod gi duongʼ kod luor, chiengʼ ma Yesu Kristo ofwenyore.  
\v 8 Kata obedo ni pok unene to pod uhere ahera kendo kata obedo ni ok unene kata sani to pod uyie ayiea kuome kendo upongʼ gi mor maduongʼ.  
\v 9 Nikech koro uyudo thoro mar yie maru, ma en warruok mar chunyu. 
\p  
\v 10 Kuom wach warruokni ema ne jonabi onono matut kendo omanyo matek, kane gikoro wach gweth mane Nyasaye biro miyou.  
\v 11 Roho mar Kristo mane nikuomgi nonyisogi chon kuom masiche mane Kristo biro yudo kod duongʼ mane biro luwo masichego, omiyo ne gitemo manyo kinde mane gigo biro timoree kendo kaka negibiro timore.  
\v 12 Nofweny nigi ni tich mane gitiyo ne ok giti nigin giwegi, to negitiyo mana ne un kane giwuoyo kuom gik makoro osenyisu gi joma oseyalonu Injili kuom teko mar Roho Maler moa e polo. Kata malaike bende gombo mondo one. 
\s1 Bedo maler 
\p  
\v 13 Emomiyo ikuru pachu ne tich. Beduru mos kendo keturu genou duto kuom ngʼwono mibiro miu ka Yesu Kristo ofwenyore.  
\v 14 Kaka nyithindo mawinjo wach, kik ulu kit gombo maricho mane uluwo chon kane pod udak e kia.  
\v 15 To mana kaka Jal moluongou ler, beduru maler e gimoro amora mutimo;  
\v 16 nikech ondiki niya, “Beduru maler nikech aler.”\f + \fr 1:16 \ft \xt Lawi 11:44,45; 19:2\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Kaka uluongo nying Wuoro mangʼado bura ne tich ngʼato ka ngʼato machalre ka ok odew wangʼ ngʼato, daguru kaka welo e piny-ka, kod luor mowinjore.  
\v 18 Nimar ungʼeyo ni kane owaru kuom ngimau manono mane kwereu machon owenu mondo ulu, to ne ok owaru gi gik makethore kaka fedha kata dhahabu,  
\v 19 makmana nowaru gi remo ma nengone tek mar Kristo, ma en Nyarombo maonge songa moro amora.  
\v 20 Ne oyiere kapok ochwe piny, to ne ofwenynwago e ndalogi mogik nikech un.  
\v 21 Nikech En, koro uyie kuom Nyasaye, mane ochiere oa kuom joma otho mi omiye duongʼ mondo yie maru kod geno maru obed kuom Nyasaye. 
\p  
\v 22 Kaka koro usepwodhuru uwegi kuom luwo adiera, mondo eka uher joweteu, koro herreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato gihera matut, kendo timuru kamano gi chunyu duto.  
\v 23 Nikech osenywolu nywol manyien, ok gi kodhi ma towo, to gi kodhi ma ok tow, gi wach Nyasaye mangima kendo mochwere.  
\v 24 Nimar Ndiko wacho niya, 
\q1 “Dhano duto chalo gi lum 
\q2 kendo duongʼ ma gin-go chalo mana gi maua manie pap; 
\q1 lum ner kendo maua two mi lwar piny, 
\q2  
\v 25 to wach Ruoth osiko manyaka chiengʼ.”\f + \fr 1:25 \ft \xt Isa 40:6-8\f* 
\m Ma e Injili mane oyalnu. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Emomiyo weuru timbe maricho duto kod wuondruok duto, kod dondruok, gi nyiego kod kuoth e yo moro amora.  
\v 2 Mana kaka nyithindo mayom, beduru gi siso gi chak mayom mar chuny mondo kumadhe to omi udongi e yor warruok,  
\v 3 nikech koro usebilo Ruoth mi uyudo ni ober. 
\s1 Kidi mangima kod joma oyier 
\p  
\v 4 Ka ubiro ir Jalno ma en Kidi mangima mane jogedo odagi, to en ema Nyasaye noyiere kendo omiye duongʼ.  
\v 5 Un bende biuru ire kaka kite mangima, mondo oger kodu hekalu mar chuny mondo ubed jodolo maler machiwo misango mag chuny ma Nyasaye oyiego kuom Yesu Kristo.  
\v 6 Mana kaka Muma wacho niya, 
\q1 “Neuru, aketo kidi e Sayun, 
\q2 en kidi moyier kendo ma nengone tek moriwo kor ot, 
\q1 to ngʼat mogeno kuome 
\q2 ok none wichkuot.”\f + \fr 2:6 \ft \xt Isa 28:16\f* 
\m  
\v 7 Kidini nigi nengo matek mana ni un joma oyie. To kuom joma ok oyie to, 
\q1 “Kidi mane jogedo odagi 
\q2 koro osedoko kidi moriwo kor ot,”\f + \fr 2:7 \ft \xt Zab 118:22\f* 
\m  
\v 8 bende niya, 
\q1 “En e kidi machwanyo ji 
\q2 kendo lwanda mamiyo gipodho.”\f + \fr 2:8 \ft \xt Isa 8:14\f* 
\m Gichwanyore nikech gitamore winjo wach mane Nyasaye owalonegi. 
\p  
\v 9 Un to un jogo moyier. Un jodolo ma joka Ruoth kendo un oganda maler mar Nyasaye mane oyiero mondo ohul tijene miwuoro, kane oluongou mi ua e mudho kendo udonjo e lerne miwuoro.  
\v 10 Chon ne ok un ji, to koro un jo-Nyasaye, chon ne pok okechu, to koro osekechu. 
\p  
\v 11 Joherana, ajiwou, kaka jowuoth kendo kaka welo e pinyni, mondo uwe gombo maricho mag ringruok makedo gi chunyu.  
\v 12 Daguru e ngima maber e kind jopiny makia Nyasaye mondo kata ka gihangonu ni un joketho to gine mana timbeu mabeyo mi gimi Nyasaye duongʼ chiengʼ ma obiro ngʼadoe bura. 
\s1 Winjo joloch kod ruodhi 
\p  
\v 13 Ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomu nyaka winj joloch duto moketi mondo orit ji, nikech uhero Ruoth Yesu madwaro ni utim kamano. Rituru chike mag ruoth marito piny,  
\v 14 kendo rituru bende chike mag jotelo ma gin joma ruoth owuon ema oketo mondo okum joma ketho to opwo joma timo maber.  
\v 15 Nikech en dwaro Nyasaye mondo timbeu mabeyo okuod wi joma ofuwo mohero weche manono.  
\v 16 Daguru ka joma ni thuolo, to kik uti gi thuolo ma un-go obed gima uumogo richou, daguru kaka jotich Nyasaye.  
\v 17 Chiwuru luor mowinjore ne ji duto. Heruru jowete duto mowar. Luoruru Nyasaye. Miuru ruoth mar piny luor. 
\p  
\v 18 To un wasumbini winjuru ruodhiu kendo migiuru luor. Kik uluor mana ruodhi mabeyo ma ok kwiny kodu, to luoruru koda mago makwiny kodu.  
\v 19 Nikech en gima ber ka dhano oyie tingʼo rem mar chandruok moyudo kayiem nikech ongʼeyo ni Nyasaye ni kode.  
\v 20 To ere kaka ngʼato diyud pak ka uyudo chwat michwadougo nikech ujoketho? To ka isandou nikech tim maber ma utimo, kendo ka unano e bwo sand ma kamano, to Nyasaye pwoyou.  
\v 21 Mano e kit ngima mane oluongue nikech Kristo nosandi nikech un, mine oweyonu ranyisi mondo un bende uluw timne. 
\q1  
\v 22 Muma wacho niya, “Ne ok otimo richo kata achiel, 
\q2 kendo onge miriambo mane owuok e dhoge.”\f + \fr 2:22 \ft \xt Isa 53:9\f* 
\m  
\v 23 Kane oyanye to ne ok oyenyo, kata kane isande to ne ok okwongʼo joma ne sande. Kar timo kamano to noketo genone kuom Jal ma jangʼad bura ma kare.  
\v 24 En owuon notingʼo richowa e ringre kane otho e msalaba mondo eka wan wadok joma otho ne richo, to wabed mangima ne timbe makare; kuom moriemo mage ema osechangu.\f + \fr 2:24 \ft \xt Isa 53:5\f* 
\v 25 Ne uchalo mana ka rombe morwenyo,\f + \fr 2:25 \ft \xt Isa 53:6\f* to koro oseduogu e yo mondo ulu Jakwadhu kendo Jarit mar chunyu. 
\c 3  
\s1 Mon kod chwo 
\p  
\v 1 Kamano un bende mon luoruru chwou, mondo ka moko kuomgi pok oyie to gilokre, ok nikech wecheu to nikech timbeu maler,  
\v 2 ka gineno bidhruok gi luor mar ngimau.  
\v 3 Ber maru ok onego onenre mana kuom gik mulichogo dendu ma oko: kaka kado wich gi rwako bangli mag dhahabu kod lewni ma nengogi tek.  
\v 4 To chutho ber maru onego obed mano maiye, ma en ber madier mar chuny mamuol kendo mokwe ma en gima duongʼ moloyo e wangʼ Nyasaye.  
\v 5 Nikech kamano e kaka mon maler machon mane oketo genogi kuom Nyasaye ne loso bergi maiye. Ne giwinjo wach chwogi,  
\v 6 mana kaka Sara, mane winjo Ibrahim kendo luonge ni ruodhe. Un udoko nyige ka utimo gik mabeyo gi chir ma ok uluoro gimoro. 
\p  
\v 7 Un chwo bende nyaka udag gi mondeu kuweyonegi korgi. Migiuru luor kaka chwech mangʼaw kendo kaka jouteu muchamogo mich mar ngima momiu kuom ngʼwono. Kutimo kamano to onge gima biro mono lemou chopo e nyim Nyasaye. 
\s1 Neno sand kuom timo maber 
\p  
\v 8 Mogik, neuru ni un duto un gi chuny achiel kod paro achiel, kuheroru kaka owete, kendo beduru mamuol kendo mangʼwon.  
\v 9 Kik uchul richo kar richo, kata ayany kar ayany kar timo kamano to gwedhuru agwedha, nikech mano omiyo noluongou, mondo uyud gweth.  
\v 10 Mana kaka Muma wacho niya, 
\q1 “Ngʼato angʼata mohero ngima 
\q2 kendo ni gigeno kuom ndalo mabiro mabeyo, 
\q1 nyaka ogengʼ lewe kik wuo marach 
\q2 kendo ogengʼ dhoge kuom wacho miriambo. 
\q1  
\v 11 Nyaka olokre owe timbe maricho mi otim tim maber; 
\q2 nyaka omany kwe kendo oluwe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Nikech wangʼ Jehova Nyasaye ni kuom joma kare 
\q2 kendo ite winjo lamogi, 
\q1 to Jehova Nyasaye mon gi joma timo gik maricho.”\f + \fr 3:12 \ft \xt Zab 34:12-16\f* 
\p  
\v 13 Ere ngʼama dihinyu ka uikoru mar timo gima ber?  
\v 14 To kata ka ochuno ni nyaka une sand kuom gima kare mutimo, to un joma ogwedhi. “Kik uluor gik ma giluoro, kendo kata bwok kik ubwogi.”\f + \fr 3:14 \ft \xt Isa 8:12\f* 
\v 15 To miuru Kristo duongʼ ei chunyu kaka Ruoth Maler. Beduru moikore kinde duto mar dwoko ngʼato mopenjou gimomiyo un gi geno ma un-gono. To timuru kamano gi muolo kod luor.  
\v 16 Rituru chunyu maler maonge bura, mondo timbeu mabeyo kuom Kristo okuod wi joma wuoyo kuomu marach.  
\v 17 En gima ber ka en dwaro Nyasaye, mondo osand ngʼato kuom timo maber moloyo ka ngʼato yudo sand kuom timo richo.  
\v 18 Nikech Kristo notho ni richo dichiel kendo mogik, ngʼat makare notho kar joma richo mondo okelu ir Nyasaye. Ne oneg ringre, to kata kamano nomiye bedo mangima kuom Roho.  
\v 19 Kuom mano, nodhi moyalo ne chunje manie twech,  
\v 20 mane otamore winjo Nyasaye chon gi lala kane Nyasaye orito amingʼa e kinde mane Nowa hondhoe yie. Ji manok kende maromo ji aboro, ema ne okwo kokalo e pi e yieno.  
\v 21 Pigno en ranyisi mar batiso makoro warou sani, batiso ok en golo chilo kuom ringruok, to en singruok motim ne Nyasaye gi chuny maler. Owarou kuom chier mar Yesu Kristo,  
\v 22 moseidho e polo kendo koro obet e bat korachwich mar Nyasaye, ka malaike duto gi loch kod teko duto winjo chikne. 
\c 4  
\s1 Dak kuom Nyasaye 
\p  
\v 1 Emomiyo kaka Kristo noneno sand e ringruok, un bende nyaka umanru gi paro machal gi mare, nikech ngʼat maneno sand e ringre koro oseloyo richo.  
\v 2 Kuom mano, un koro ok udak e ngima maru mar pinyni mondo uchop gombo maricho mag dhano, to udak mar timo dwaro Nyasaye.  
\v 3 Nikech ne un gi kinde malach mokadho, nutimo gik ma jopiny ohero timo kaka: dwanyruok, gombo, mer, tugo e thum, math mar anjawo kod lamo nyiseche manono.  
\v 4 To tinde ka ok uriwru gi joma kamago e oowruok mar ngima monjawni, to giwuoro kendo giyanyou.  
\v 5 Giko to nyaka ni ginihul wach man kuomgi giwegi ni Jal moikore mar ngʼado bura ni joma ngima gi joma otho.  
\v 6 Mano emomiyo ne oyal Injili nyaka ni joma koro osetho, mondo eka obi ongʼadnegi bura, kaka nongʼad ni ji duto manie ringruok, to chunygi mondo obed mangima kaluwore gi dwaro Nyasaye. 
\p  
\v 7 Giko gik moko duto chiegni. Emomiyo beduru gi paro maler kendo ritreuru mondo ulam.  
\v 8 To moloyo mago duto, herreuru gihera matut ngʼato gi ngʼato, nikech hera umo richo mangʼeny.  
\v 9 Rwakuru joweteu ma ok ungʼur.  
\v 10 Ngʼato ka ngʼato mondo oti kod mich moro amora mosemiye mondo okonygo jomoko. Ka utiyo gi kinda kaka jorit mag ngʼwono mopogore opogore ma Nyasaye omiyo kuom konyo ji.  
\v 11 Ka ngʼato en jaland wach, to wach molando Obed mana mar Nyasaye kende. Ka ngʼato tiyo ni ji, to onego otim kamano gi teko ma Nyasaye chiwo, mondo kuom gik moko duto ji opak Nyasaye kuom Yesu Kristo. Duongʼ gi teko mondo obed mare mochwere manyaka chiengʼ. Amin. 
\s1 Sand kuom bedo ja-Kristo 
\p  
\v 12 Osiepena mahero, kik uluor ka uyudo sand mawangʼou ka mach kuparo ni gimoro magalagala ema timorenu.  
\v 13 To beduru mamor nikech uriworu kod Kristo e sandne, mondo unudok moil chuth chiengʼ ma duongʼne nofwenyre.  
\v 14 Ka iyanyou nikech nying Kristo to kwanreuru kaka joma ogwedhi, nikech Roho mar duongʼ kendo mar Nyasaye ni kuomu.  
\v 15 Ka ngʼato kuomu neno sand to kik bed nikech ojanek kata ojakuo, kata en ja-mahundu, kata ojaketre e weche ji.  
\v 16 To ka uyudo sand nikech un jo-Kristo to kik wiyi kuodi, to gone Nyasaye erokamano nikech iluongou gi nyingno.  
\v 17 Nikech ndalo koro osechopo mingʼadoe bura ni jood Nyasaye. To ka wan ema ochakore kodwa kamano to uparo ni joma ok luw Injili mar Nyasaye to biro neno malit machal nadi?  
\v 18 Nikech Muma wacho niya, 
\q1 “Ka en gima tek mondo owar joma timbegi beyo, 
\q2 koro joma kia Nyasaye gi joricho to nobed machalo nadi?”\f + \fr 4:18 \ft \xt Nge 11:31\f* 
\p  
\v 19 Kuom mano joma neno sand kaluwore gi dwaro mar Nyasaye onego ochiw chunygi e lwet Jachwech ma ja-adiera kendo onego gidhi nyime gi timo timbe mabeyo. 
\c 5  
\s1 Puonj kuom jodongo kod jomatindo 
\p  
\v 1 Ne jodongo man e dieru akwayou kaka jaduongʼ wadu mane janeno kaka Kristo sandore, kendo kaka achiel kuom joma biro yudo duongʼ mabiro fwenyore achien:  
\v 2 Beduru jokwath mag kweth Nyasaye moseketo e lwetu mondo uriti. Ritgiuru kaka jorit, ok nikech ngʼato ochunou, to nikech chunyu ohero, kaka Nyasaye dwaro ni utim. Kik ubed jokwath mondo uyudie ohala, to timuru kamano nikech uhero.  
\v 3 Kik utimru ruodhi ewi joma oketi e lwetu mondo uriti, to bedne giuru ranyisi maber.  
\v 4 To ka Jakwath Maduongʼ obiro to unuyud osimbo mar duongʼ ma ok kethre ma nosik karieny nyaka chiengʼ. 
\p  
\v 5 Un jomatindo bende chiwuru luor ni jomadongo. Rwakreuru gi muolo e kindu ngʼato gi ngʼato, nikech Muma wacho niya, 
\q1 “Nyasaye osin gi josunga 
\q2 to ochiwo ngʼwono ne joma muol.”\f + \fr 5:5 \ft \xt Nge 3:34\f* 
\m  
\v 6 Emomiyo beduru joma obolore e bwo bad Nyasaye man-gi teko eka enotingʼu malo e kinde mowinjore.  
\v 7 Keturu parruok duto ma un-go kuome nikech oparou. 
\p  
\v 8 Beduru motangʼ ka ungʼeyo ni jasiku, ma en Satan, bayo kuonde duto mana ka sibuor maruto, komanyo ngʼama dongam.  
\v 9 Chungʼuru motegno kuom yie ma un-go kendo tameuru, nikech ungʼeyo ni joweteu moyie e piny ngima bende neno chandruok machal gi ma uneno. 
\p  
\v 10 Ka useneno chandruok kuom kinde moromo, Nyasach ngʼwono duto, mane oluongou e duongʼne mochwere kuom Kristo Yesu, nomi ubed maler chuth, kogurou udoko motegno e mise ma ok yiengni.  
\v 11 Duongʼ odogne ndalo duto manyaka chiengʼ. Amin. 
\b  
\s1 Mos mogik 
\p  
\v 12 Andikonu baruwa machwokni ka Sila,\f + \fr 5:12 \ft Jo-Grik luonge ni \fqa Silfano.\f* ma akwano kaka owadwa madier kuom Kristo, konya. Ajiwou kendo atimo neno ni ma e kaka ngʼwono madier mar Nyasaye chalo, omiyo chunguru motegno kuom ngʼwonono. 
\b  
\p  
\v 13 Kanyakla mar jo-Kristo man Babulon, ma Nyasaye oyiero kaachiel kodu, okowonu mos. Wuoda Mariko bende omosou. 
\p  
\v 14 Mosreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato gi yogruok mar hera. 
\b  
\p Kwe mondo obed kodu un duto ma un kuom Kristo.